---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";

---

<title>Career</title>
<body>
<main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
<Layout>
    <div class="w-full md:h-auto p-4 mt-10">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-1 grid-rows-2 gap-4">
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-[#70fe90] font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Join Our Team of Innovators</h2>
                <p class="p-1 text-[#e5eae6] mb-6 text-justify">We are passionate about creating innovative digital marketing solutions and exceptional web experiences for our clients. Our team is a diverse group of talented professionals who thrive on creativity, collaboration, and cutting-edge technology. If you’re driven, forward-thinking, and ready to make an impact in the digital world, we want to hear from you.</p>
                
                <h2 class="text-[#70fe90] font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Why Work With Us?</h2>
                <p class="p-1 text-[#e5eae6] mb-6 text-justify">
                    - <b>Innovation at the Core</b>:<br/> We foster a culture of continuous learning and innovation. You'll have the opportunity to work on exciting projects that push the boundaries of digital marketing, web design, UI/UX, advertising, and content creation.<br/>
                    - <b>Collaborative Environment</b>:<br/> Our team-oriented approach ensures that your voice is heard, and your ideas are valued. We believe in working together to achieve extraordinary results.<br/>
                    - <b>Professional Growth</b>:<br/> We are committed to your career development. Whether it's through mentorship, training programs, or hands-on project experience, we support your growth every step of the way.<br/>
                    - <b>Flexible Work Arrangements</b>:<br/> We understand the importance of work-life balance. Our flexible work policies and remote work options help you manage your personal and professional commitments effectively.<br/>
                    - <b>Competitive Compensation</b>:<br/> We offer attractive salaries, benefits, and performance-based bonuses to recognize and reward your hard work and dedication.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-[#70fe90] font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Current Openings</h2>
                <p class="p-1 text-[#e5eae6] mb-6 text-justify">
                    1. <b>Digital Marketing Specialist</b> :<br/>
                    - Develop and execute digital marketing campaigns across various platforms.<br/>
                    - Analyze campaign performance and optimize for better results.<br/>
                    - Collaborate with the content creation team to produce engaging content.<br/>
                    - Requirements: Bachelor’s degree in Marketing or related field, 2+ years of experience.<br/>
                    2. <b>Web Developer</b> : <br/>
                    - Design, develop, and maintain high-quality websites.<br/>
                    - Ensure websites are responsive, fast, and secure.<br/>
                    - Work closely with the UI/UX team to implement designs.<br/>
                    - Requirements: Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science or related field, proficiency in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and experience with CMS platforms.<br/>

                    3. <b>UI/UX Designer</b> :<br/>
                    - Create intuitive and visually appealing user interfaces.<br/>
                    - Conduct user research and testing to inform design decisions.<br/>
                    - Collaborate with developers to ensure design feasibility.<br/>
                    - Requirements: Bachelor’s degree in Design or related field, strong portfolio demonstrating UI/UX design skills.<br/>

                    4. <b>Content Creator</b> :<br/>
                    - Develop engaging and original content for blogs, social media, and websites.<br/>
                    - Work with the marketing team to align content with campaign goals.<br/>
                    - Edit and proofread content to ensure high quality.<br/>
                    - Requirements: Bachelor’s degree in English, Communications, or related field, exceptional writing and editing skills.
                </p>
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-[#70fe90] font-semibold text-lg mb-2">How to Apply</h2>
                <p class="p-1 text-[#e5eae6] mb-6 text-justify">To apply for any of our open positions, please send your resume, cover letter, and portfolio (if applicable) to contact@alima.agency. In your cover letter, tell us why you’re passionate about joining Alima Agency and how you can contribute to our team.
                    We look forward to hearing from you and exploring how your skills and experiences align with our vision and values.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 border-t border-white pt-8 sm:mt-4 lg:mt-4"></div>
    <div class="m-auto justify-center items-center text-center">
        <h2 class="text-[#70fe90] font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="p-1 text-[#e5eae6] mb-6 text-center">If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at:<br/>
            <br/>
            <span class="font-semibold">
            <span class="text-[#70fe90]">A</span>lima Agency <br/>
            <span class="text-[#70fe90]">contact</span>@alima.agency<br/>
            <span class="text-[#70fe90]">support</span>@alima.agency<br/>
            <span class="text-[#70fe90]">marketing</span>@alima.agency<br/>
            <span class="text-[#70fe90]">engineering</span>@alima.agency<br/> 
            021-2222222</p></span>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 mb-10 border-t border-white pt-8 sm:mt-4 lg:mt-4"></div>
</Layout>
</main>
</body>